Interface IPokedex

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IPokemonFactory, IPokemonMetadataProvider
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PokedexImplement

    public interface IPokedex
extends IPokemonMetadataProvider, IPokemonFactory
    IPokedex interface. An IPokedex aims to store all information about captured pokemon, as their default metadata as well.
    Author:
    fv
